Enum Constant Detail

NONE

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType NONE
This notification is for internal or future use.

OUT_BID

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType OUT_BID
This notification is sent to a subscribed buyer when another buyer has outbid (placed a higher maximum bid) the subscribed buyer on an auction listing, and the subscribed buyer is no longer the current high bidder.

This notification is only applicable for auction listings.

END_OF_AUCTION

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType END_OF_AUCTION
This notification is sent to all subscribed bidders of an auction item and to the subscribed seller of the auction item as soon as the auction listing ends with or without a winning bidder. This notification will also be sent to subscribed bidders and the subscribed seller if a buyer ends the auction as a result of using the auction listing's Buy It Now feature.

This notification is only applicable for auction listings.

AUCTION_CHECKOUT_COMPLETE

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType AUCTION_CHECKOUT_COMPLETE
This notification is sent to the subscribed seller when the winning bidder or buyer has paid for the auction or fixed-price item and completed the checkout process.

For multiple line item orders, an AuctionCheckoutComplete notification is only generated for one of the line items in the order. In this case, the seller would look for the containing order number for the line item in the Transaction.ContainingOrder.OrderID field, and then make a GetOrders call (using the container order ID as an input filter) to retrieve complete information for the order.

CHECKOUT_BUYER_REQUESTS_TOTAL

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType CHECKOUT_BUYER_REQUESTS_TOTAL
This notification is sent to a subscribed seller when a buyer/winning bidder is requesting a total price before paying for the item.

This notification is applicable for auction listings and for fixed-price listings that do not require immediate payment.

FEEDBACK

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType FEEDBACK
This notification is sent to a subsribed buyer or seller when that buyer or seller has left Feedback for the other party in the order, or has received Feedback from the other party in the order.

This notification is applicable for all listing types and orders.

FEEDBACK_FOR_SELLER

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType FEEDBACK_FOR_SELLER
This notification is deprecated.

Use the Feedback notification instead.

FIXED_PRICE_TRANSACTION

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType FIXED_PRICE_TRANSACTION
This notification is sent to a subscribed seller each time a buyer purchases an item in a multiple-quantity, fixed-price listing. In the case of a single-quantity, fixed-price listing, the 'ItemSold' notification will be sent to the seller instead of 'FixedPriceTransaction'.

This notification is only applicable for multiple-quantity, fixed-price listings.

SECOND_CHANCE_OFFER

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType SECOND_CHANCE_OFFER
This notification is sent to a subscribed buyer who was unsuccessful in winning an auction item, but who is now receiving a Second Chance Offer from the seller of the original item. A seller may send a Second Chance Offer to a potential buyer if that seller was unable to complete the sale with the winning bidder or if that seller has duplicate items for sale.

This notification is only applicable for auction listings.

ASK_SELLER_QUESTION

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType ASK_SELLER_QUESTION
This notification is sent to a subscribed seller when an eBay user has used the Ask a question feature on the seller's active listing. An eBay user does not have to be an active bidder on an auction listing to ask a seller a question.

This notification is applicable to auction and fixed-priced listings.

ITEM_LISTED

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType ITEM_LISTED
This notification is sent to a subscribed seller each time one of the subscribed seller's items is listed or relisted. This notification is also triggered when the Unpaid Item Assistant mechanism relists an item for the seller.

This notification is applicable to auction and fixed-priced listings.

ITEM_REVISED

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType ITEM_REVISED
This notification is sent to a subscribed seller when one of the subscribed seller's items is revised.

This notification is applicable to auction and fixed-priced listings.

BUYER_RESPONSE_DISPUTE

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType BUYER_RESPONSE_DISPUTE
This notification is sent to a subscribed seller each time a buyer responds to an Unpaid Item or Cancel Transaction case that the subscribed seller has opened up against the buyer.

This notification is applicable to auction and fixed-priced listings.

SELLER_OPENED_DISPUTE

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType SELLER_OPENED_DISPUTE
This notification is sent to a subscribed buyer if a seller opens up an Unpaid Item or Cancel Transaction case against the subscribed buyer.

This notification is applicable to auction and fixed-priced listings.

SELLER_RESPONDED_TO_DISPUTE

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType SELLER_RESPONDED_TO_DISPUTE
This notification is sent to a subscribed buyer each time a seller responds to an Item Not Received or (Item) Significantly Not As Described case that the subscribed buyer has opened up against the seller.

This notification is applicable to auction and fixed-priced listings.

SELLER_CLOSED_DISPUTE

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType SELLER_CLOSED_DISPUTE
This notification is sent to the subscribed buyer and seller if the seller closes an Unpaid Item or Cancel Transaction case against the buyer.

This notification is applicable to auction and fixed-priced listings.

BEST_OFFER

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType BEST_OFFER
This notification is sent to a subscribed seller if a potential buyer has made a best offer on a Best Offer-enabled fixed-price or Classified Ad listing.

This notification is applicable to fixed-priced, Classified Ad, and eBay Motors Local Market listings.

MY_MESSAGES_ALERT_HEADER

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType MY_MESSAGES_ALERT_HEADER

Such requests using versions 685 and higher will return an error response.

MY_MESSAGESE_BAY_MESSAGE_HEADER

public static final NotificationEventTypeCodeType MY_MESSAGESE_BAY_MESSAGE_HEADER
This notification is sent to a subscribed user or application when a message from eBay is sent to the user's My Messages. This notification type sends a GetMyMessages response at a detail level of ReturnHeaders. MyMessageseBayMessageHeader and MyMessageseBayMessage cannot be subscribed to at the same time or specified in the same call.

Applies to both Buyers and Sellers.

MyMessageseBayMessageHeader and MyMessageseBayMessage cannot be subscribed to at the same time or specified in the same call.

Applies to both Buyers and Sellers.
